Bucket Transformations: Categorize Field Values

Bucket your number, text, and boolean fields to group and organize data.

Categorize Date Field Values into Buckets
Use a transformation to create a calculated field based on a formula. You add transformations inside a Transform node. You can string together multiple transformations to manipulate data sequentially.
Categorize Text Column Values into Buckets
Use a column field to categorize and organize text values, including email, phone, and URL. For example, to group by region, you can create the buckets West, Central, and East.
Categorize Numeric Field Values into Buckets
Use a bucket field to categorize and organize numeric values. For example, to group by region, you can create buckets High, Middle, Low to group numbers of cases per account.
